-- Billionaire Lisin’s Freight One to Name Voloshin Board Chairman
-- B y   E k a t e r i n a   S h a t a l o v a
-- 2012-01-25T11:45:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-25/alexander-voloshin-may-lead-freight-one-s-board-kommersant-says.html
Russian billionaire  Vladimir Lisin ’s
OAO Freight One rail freight operator nominated  Alexander Voloshin , former chief of staff to Prime Minister  Vladimir Putin , to become board chairman.  The company, in which Lisin bought 75 percent last month,
will hold a shareholder meeting on Feb. 10 to vote on the board,
the billionaire’s UCL Holding transportation unit said today in
an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
